```

This follows directly from the definition of cyclotomic polynomials, which are defined as factors of $X^n - 1$.

Then we have a lemma about the divisibility of $X^k - 1$ by $(X^k - 1)$ and $\phi(n)$:

```tactics
lemma phi_div_2 (n : ‚Ñï) (k : ‚Ñï) (h‚ÇÇ : k ‚à£ n) (h‚ÇÉ : k < n) :
